trans-unit.source: Represents the base item class for all the metadata in the [!INCLUDE[vstecado](~/add/includes/vstecado-md.md)] metadata type hierarchy.
trans-unit.target: Representerer base elementklassen for alle metadataene i den [!INCLUDE[vstecado](~/add/includes/vstecado-md.md)] metadata typehierarki.

trans-unit.source: Gets the built-in type kind for this type.
trans-unit.target: Henter innebygd type-type for denne typen.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind"></xref> object that represents the built-in type kind for this type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind"> </xref> objektet som representerer innebygd type-type for denne typen.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets the documentation associated with this type.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir dokumentasjonen som er forbundet med denne typen.

trans-unit.source: This property allows you to get and set the <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.Documentation> object that represents the documentation associated with conceptual model constructs such as the <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EntityContainer>, the <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EntityType>, the <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ComplexType>, the <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType>, and so on.
trans-unit.target: Denne egenskapen kan du hente og angi det <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.Documentation>objektet som representerer dokumentasjonen tilknyttet begrepsmodell konstruksjoner som den <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EntityContainer>, <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EntityType>, <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ComplexType>, <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType>og så videre.</xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.AssociationType> </xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ComplexType> </xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EntityType> </xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EntityContainer> </xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.Documentation>

trans-unit.source: You can define the documentation tag in the conceptual schema definition language (CSDL) files and store schema definition language (SSDL) files.
trans-unit.target: Du kan definere koden dokumentasjonen i begrepsmodellen skjemaet definition language (CSDL) filene og lagre filer i skjemaet definition language (SSDL).
Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se [dokumentasjonen elementet (CSDL)](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d49e7bb9-a6a1-4017-9c7e-7836bf3bef48).

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.Documentation"></xref> object that represents the documentation on this type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.Documentation"> </xref> objektet som representerer dokumentasjonen for denne typen.

trans-unit.source: Returns a conceptual model built-in type that matches one of the <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind"></xref> values.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en innebygd begrepsmodelltypen som tilsvarer en av <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.BuiltInTypeKind"> </xref> verdier.

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmType"></xref> object that represents the built-in type in the EDM.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Data.Metadata.Edm.EdmType"> </xref> objektet som representerer innebygd type i EDM.

trans-unit.source: Returns the list of the general facet descriptions for a specified type.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer den generelle Fasett beskrivelse for en angitt type.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> object that represents the list of the general facet descriptions for a specified type.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Collections.ObjectModel.ReadOnlyCollection%601> objektet som representerer listen over generelle Fasett beskrivelse for en angitt type.

trans-unit.source: Gets the list of properties of the current type.
trans-unit.target: Henter listen over egenskaper av typen gjeldende.
Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, kan du se <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.MetadataProperty>.</xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.MetadataProperty>

trans-unit.source: A collection of type <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection%601> that contains the list of properties of the current type.
trans-unit.target: En samling av typen <xref:System.Data.Metadata.Edm.ReadOnlyMetadataCollection%601> som inneholder listen over egenskaper av typen gjeldende.
